org.springframework.data.redis.connection.jedis

接口 JedisClientConfiguration


  • public interface JedisClientConfiguration
    Redis client configuration for jedis. This configuration provides optional configuration elements such as SSLSocketFactory and JedisPoolConfig specific to jedis client features.

    Providing optional elements allows a more specific configuration of the client:

    • Whether to use SSL
    • Optional SSLSocketFactory
    • Optional SSLParameters
    • Optional HostnameVerifier
    • Whether to use connection-pooling
    • Optional GenericObjectPoolConfig
    • Connect timeout
    • Read timeout
    从以下版本开始:
    2.0
    另请参阅:
    redis.clients.jedis.Jedis, RedisStandaloneConfiguration, RedisSentinelConfiguration, RedisClusterConfiguration
